label: specifiedProcessCertificate
comment: A process certificate for this specified chemical treatment.

rangeIncludes.comment: A piece of written, printed or electronic matter that provides information or evidence that a process has met required criteria.

domainIncludes.comment: Any substance such as dyestuffs, chrome oxide, acids, sulphate, surfactant or other chemicals applied to an agricultural field, substrate, plant, animal product, material or product.
